## Architecture

```
User (voice/text)
    -> VoiceEngine / UI CommandInput
    -> CommandRouter
    -> Policy Guardrails (evaluate)
    -> Intent Classifier
    -> Integrations (browser, apps, search, news, weather)
    -> Response (UI + TTS)

Background Listener (separate process)
    -> STT wake detection
    -> launcher.activate_friday()
    -> IPC (pending_command.txt, wake_signal)
```

---

## Main Modules

| Module | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `friday/main.py` | Qt app entry, wires UI + voice + IPC |
| `friday/config.py` | Settings persistence |
| `friday/policy/guardrails.py` | File-access blocker |
| `friday/core/router.py` | Command dispatch |
| `friday/core/intents.py` | Intent classification |
| `friday/voice/engine.py` | In-app voice loop |
| `friday/background_listener.py` | Always-on wake listener |
| `friday/launcher.py` | Launch/focus GUI |
| `friday/ipc.py` | Inter-process files |
| `friday/integrations/*` | External services |

